        "category": "special",
        "power": 50,
        "accuracy": 95,
        "description": "<p>Effect: On hit, the target has a 20% chance of gaining @Affliction[poison 3] and losing -1 SPDEF Stage for 3 Activations.</p><p>For each consecutive time this attack is used and hits at least one target, this Attack's Power increases by 20, its Accuracy decreases by -5, its effect chances are increased by +10% and their duration increases by +1. This progress is tracked by the Clock named for this Attack.</p><p>This Clock resets if the user fails to hit at least one target with this Attack, leaves combat, gains @Affliction[fainted], or combat ends.</p>",
